Package: org.grails.datastore.mapping.simpledb.engine

[Java] Class SimpleDBEntityPersister

          • org.grails.datastore.mapping.simpledb.engine.SimpleDBEntityPersister

          • A org.grails.datastore.mapping.engine.EntityPersister implementation for the SimpleDB store.

            Authors:
            Roman Stepanenko based on Graeme Rocher code for MongoDb and Redis
            Since:
            0.1

            • Nested Class Summary

                Nested classes 
                Modifiers Name Description
                protected class  SimpleDBEntityPersister.SimpleDBNativeEntryModifyingEntityAccess Provides proper conversion of 'version' field from Integer to Long - since we use numeric padding in SimpleDB there are different amounts of zeros for Long and Integer - and it matters for optimistic locking assertions on SimpleDB level.
